Texts.Chs: 我探索了先驱废墟的奥秘，在这儿的每一分钟都是值得的。
Texts.Eng: I've explored the mysteries of the Precursor ruins, and it was worth every minute.

Texts.Chs: 我在哪里？尽管这个^green;数据盘^reset;有在显示坐标，但奇怪的是，这个区域一直缺乏...一切。我一定要探索这个地方。
Texts.Eng: Where am I? This ^green;data-disc^reset; at least presents the coordinates. What is odd, is that this sector has always been devoid of...everything. I should definitely explore this place.
